wibsr 0.0.1
  • Reference

Introduction

This is an R package for processing the raw data from Wideband Integrated Bioaerosol Sensors (WIBS-NEO).

Features

‘wibsr’ is an all-in-on package, which reads raw WIBS data, calculate statistics, and plot figures

Quick Start

Installation of R

Download R and install it.

Download RStudio and install it.

Installation of wibsr

Contact the author for the package.

In RStudio ID, click Tool - install packages. Choose the package file to install it.
